WEBVTT

1
01:11:22.290 --> 01:11:23.790 
- 有隐喻的作用 - 我都知道
- it's metaphor. - i know.

2
01:11:23.810 --> 01:11:25.500 
我只是想把这一幕推迟到下周而已
I know, but we can just- we can do it next week

3
01:11:25.560 --> 01:11:27.040 
- 这不会影响什么的 - 不行 格雷格
- it's not a big deal. - no, i can't, greg!

4
01:11:27.070 --> 01:11:28.260 
对不起 我不会答应你的
It's impossible. i'm sorry.

5
01:11:28.330 --> 01:11:29.070 
汤米
Tommy?

6
01:11:29.090 --> 01:11:30.680 
我没有给其他任何人特殊待遇
I can't give you special treatment, greg.

7
01:11:30.700 --> 01:11:32.950 
就连你也不例外 格雷格
When i can't give special treatment to everybody.

8
01:11:32.980 --> 01:11:34.230 
在这里的每个人 都很努力工作
Everybody here working hard.

9
01:11:34.260 --> 01:11:36.830 
我只求你这一次 以朋友的名义
One favor. i'm just asking for a tiny favor as a friend.

10
01:11:36.850 --> 01:11:39.050 
求我 求我 你总是在求我
Favor, favor, favor. you always ask favor.

11
01:11:39.070 --> 01:11:40.460 
这只是一件小事啊
This is one tiny thing, that's it!

12
01:11:40.490 --> 01:11:42.420 
我带你来洛杉矶 给你地方住
I take you to los angeles, give you place to stay.

13
01:11:42.440 --> 01:11:44.180 
我为你写剧本
I write you this part.

14
01:11:44.350 --> 01:11:46.310 
我拍这部电影就是为了你 格雷格
I do this whole movie for you, greg?

15
01:11:46.340 --> 01:11:48.450 
兄弟 你拍这部电影不是为了我
You did it for me? come on, man.

16
01:11:48.470 --> 01:11:50.460 
- 为了我们 我们是一起的 对吧 - 对 我知道
- for us? we do it together, right? - okay, i know.

17
01:11:50.490 --> 01:11:52.800 
是的 这是属于我们的电影 这一点不会改变
Yes, it's our movie. this doesn't change that.

18
01:11:52.830 --> 01:11:53.960 
别背叛我 格雷格
Don't betray me, greg.

19
01:11:53.980 --> 01:11:55.080 
我不会背叛你的
I'm not betraying you.

